    {
      "id": "PopularPost313220",
      "post_content": "R&D \"Balanced\" the Color Pie back in the day by doing this, [Boil](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Boil), and there was totally a Green effect that wrecked the tar out of Islands, but I forget it's name.  \n  \nIt was an arms race to see who cast their Color-Specific Godzilla at each other first. :P  \n  \n\"Alpha Eldrazi Blue\", \"Alpha Eldrazi Red\", \"Alpha Eldrazi Green\"  \n  \nCast Alpha Eldrazi (color) only if your opponent is playing that color.   \nWhen Alpha Eldrazi enters the battlefield, rape that color.  \n  \nI don't remember if White and Black really did this as badly. Oh sure, there was Color-Hate in all 5 colors, but it seems [Black Knight](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Black Knight) and [White Knight](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=White Knight) were in general a lot more balanced about this than [Animar](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Animar) was.",
      "posted_by": "DarthParallax",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost313220\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_post\">R&amp;D \"Balanced\" the Color Pie back in the day by doing this, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Boil\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Boil\">Boil</a>, and there was totally a Green effect that wrecked the tar out of Islands, but I forget it's name.<br/><br/>It was an arms race to see who cast their Color-Specific Godzilla at each other first. :P<br/><br/>\"Alpha Eldrazi Blue\", \"Alpha Eldrazi Red\", \"Alpha Eldrazi Green\"<br/><br/>Cast Alpha Eldrazi (color) only if your opponent is playing that color. <br/>When Alpha Eldrazi enters the battlefield, rape that color.<br/><br/>I don't remember if White and Black really did this as badly. Oh sure, there was Color-Hate in all 5 colors, but it seems <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Black Knight\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Black Knight\">Black Knight</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"White Knight\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=White Knight\">White Knight</a> were in general a lot more balanced about this than <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Animar\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Animar\">Animar</a> was.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '313220'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy46041\">DarthParallax</span>\r\n                                (4/29/2013 11:46:33 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>"
